<p>Hi there,</p>

<p>
  This is the second and final notice that your Google Workspace access for
  <code><%= @g_suite.domain %></code> will be revoked <strong>in one week
  on <%= @g_suite_revocation.scheduled_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></strong>
  because <%= @reason %>.
</p>

<% if @g_suite_revocation.because_of_other? %>
  <p>
    On this date, you will no longer be able to access Google Workspace through
    HCB and your data and accounts will be permanently deleted. Please export
    your data
    before <%= @g_suite_revocation.scheduled_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>.
  </p>
<% else %>
  <p>
    If you do not take action to remedy the issue, your data and accounts will
    be irrecoverably deleted, and you will no longer be able to access Google
    Workspace through HCB.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you no longer plan to use Google Workspace, please export your data
    before <%= @g_suite_revocation.scheduled_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>.
  </p>

  <%= render "g_suite/revocation_mailer/revocation_warning_details" %>
<% end %>

<p>
  Best,<br>
  The HCB Team
</p>
